title: Wholesale Price of Pig Iron for Dusseldorf, Germany
notes: Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1880-1914 (2)--Original Data, 1913-1935. There Are No Data For July, 1899 And March-July, 1901. Area Covered Dusseldorf District, Germany. Source: Monatshefte Zur Statistik Des Deutschen Reichs, 1879-1891 Data; Vierteljahrshefte Zur Statistik, 1893 And Thereafter For 1892-1914 Data.
